## If generating JSON for multiple samples, replace '</full/file/path>' or 'null' with '<>', then complete radia.sample_list.tab. See
## ./backup_templates/radia.sample_list.template for examples. Be certain to provide a unique identifier under the 'run_uid' header to
## clearly distinguish samples/runs. If *optional* sample-specific values are desired, the appropriate key from this template may be used as
## a column header in radia.sample_list.tab (be careful to maintain tab-delimited format).
